    <compoundname>md__home_xl_ci_gitlab-runner_builds_f5c994c2_0_software_library_cmsis-5-riscv_CMSIS_nmsis_release_NMSIS_DSP_Examples_RISCV_README</compoundname>
    <title>Run DSP Examples in Spike</title>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Here we will describe how to run the nmsis dsp examples in Nuclei Spike.</para><para><heading level="2">Preparation</heading>
</para><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Nuclei Modified Spike</para></listitem><listitem><para>Nuclei Modified PK</para></listitem><listitem><para>Nuclei RISCV GNU Toolchain</para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para><para><heading level="2">Tool Setup</heading>
</para><para><orderedlist>
<listitem><para>Export <bold>PATH</bold> correctly for <computeroutput>spike</computeroutput> and <computeroutput>riscv-nuclei-elf-gcc</computeroutput> <programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">export<sp/>PATH=/path/to/spike/bin:/path/to/riscv-nuclei-elf-gcc/bin/:$PATH</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para></listitem><listitem><para>Export <bold>PK</bold> correctly for <computeroutput>spike</computeroutput> commond. <programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">export<sp/>PK=/path/to/spike/riscv32-unknown-elf/bin/pk</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para></listitem></orderedlist>
</para><para><heading level="2">Build NMSIS DSP Library</heading>
</para><para>Follow the NMSIS DSP documentation to build and install DSP library.</para><para><heading level="2">How to run</heading>
</para><para><orderedlist>
<listitem><para>Let us take <computeroutput>./riscv_class_marks_example/</computeroutput> for example</para></listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput>cd ./riscv_class_marks_example/</computeroutput></para></listitem><listitem><para>Run with RISCV DSP enabled NMSIS-DSP library <programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">make<sp/>DSP_ENABLE=ON<sp/>-B<sp/>run</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para></listitem><listitem><para>Run with RISCV DSP disabled NMSIS-DSP library <programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">make<sp/>DSP_ENABLE=OFF<sp/>-B<sp/>run</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para></listitem></orderedlist>
</para>    </detaileddescription>
